      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prs-stp-orc-900.
       prs-stp-orc-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore letto in work personalizzazioni          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      s-alf                to   w-prs-soc-str          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valori letti                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si/No riga aggiuntiva per stampa codice     *
      *                  * prodotto                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-soc-rac        not  = "N" and
                     w-prs-soc-rac        not  = "C" and
                     w-prs-soc-rac        not  = "P" and
                     w-prs-soc-rac        not  = "f"
                     move  "N"            to   w-prs-soc-rac          .
       prs-stp-orc-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     prs-stp-orc-999.
       prs-stp-orc-999.
           exit.

