      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        s-ves                =    spaces
                     move  s-alf          to   w-ref-int-frm-des
                                              (w-ref-int-frm-ctr)
           else      move  spaces         to   w-ref-int-frm-des
                                              (w-ref-int-frm-ctr)     .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     ref-int-frm-500.
       ref-int-frm-999.
           exit.

