      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-box-tes-doc-tit    =    spaces
                     go to box-tes-doc-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione stringa                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-box-tes-doc-x40      .
           move      1                    to   w-box-tes-doc-pnt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Trattino iniziale                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
