                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-box-tes-doc-x40
                                  with pointer w-box-tes-doc-pnt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Contenuto titolo                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           string    w-box-tes-doc-tit
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-box-tes-doc-x40
                                  with pointer w-box-tes-doc-pnt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riposizionamento all'ultimo non-blank   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-box-tes-doc-ctr      .
           inspect   w-box-tes-doc-x40    
                                      tallying w-box-tes-doc-ctr
                                          for  trailing spaces        .
           subtract  w-box-tes-doc-ctr    from 40
                                        giving w-box-tes-doc-pnt      .
           add       1                    to   w-box-tes-doc-pnt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Trattino finale                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
